      @Query(value=" SELECT MIN(p.price) AS min, MAX(p.price) AS max FROM products p\n LEFT JOIN products_colors pc ON pc.product_id = p.id\n LEFT JOIN colors c ON pc.colors_id = c.id\n JOIN products_features pf on p.id = pf.product_id\n JOIN features f on f.id = pf.features_id\n JOIN products_sports ps on p.id = ps.product_id\n JOIN sports s on ps.sports_id = s.id\n WHERE p.deleted = false AND\n (:sports IS NULL OR s.name IN :sports) AND\n (:colors IS NULL OR c.name IN :colors) AND\n (:features IS NULL OR f.name IN :features) AND\n (:countries IS NULL OR p.country_of_origin IN :countries) AND\n (:brands IS NULL OR p.brand IN :brands) AND\n (:sizeUS IS NULL OR p.sizeus IN :sizeUS) AND\n (:sizeUK IS NULL OR p.sizeuk IN :sizeUK) AND\n (:sizeEUR IS NULL OR p.sizeeur IN :sizeEUR) AND\n (:query IS NULL OR p.name ILIKE CONCAT(\'%\', :query, \'%\'))\n", nativeQuery=true) ProductsRepository.PriceRangeProjection findPriceRange(Collection<String> sports, Collection<String> colors, Collection<String> features, Collection<String> countries, Collection<String> brands, Collection<Double> sizeUS, Collection<Double> sizeEUR, Collection<Double> sizeUK, String query)

      @Query(value=" SELECT DISTINCT p.* FROM products p\n LEFT JOIN products_colors pc ON pc.product_id = p.id\n LEFT JOIN colors c ON pc.colors_id = c.id\n JOIN products_features pf on p.id = pf.product_id\n JOIN features f on f.id = pf.features_id\n JOIN products_sports ps on p.id = ps.product_id\n JOIN sports s on ps.sports_id = s.id\n WHERE p.deleted = false AND\n (:sports IS NULL OR s.name IN :sports) AND\n (:colors IS NULL OR c.name IN :colors) AND\n (:features IS NULL OR f.name IN :features) AND\n (:countries IS NULL OR p.country_of_origin IN :countries) AND\n (:brands IS NULL OR p.brand IN :brands) AND\n (:sizeUS IS NULL OR p.sizeus IN :sizeUS) AND\n (:sizeEUR IS NULL OR p.sizeeur IN :sizeEUR) AND\n (:sizeUK IS NULL OR p.sizeuk IN :sizeUK) AND\n (:minPrice IS NULL OR p.price >= :minPrice) AND\n (:maxPrice IS NULL OR p.price <= :maxPrice) AND\n (:query IS NULL OR p.name ILIKE CONCAT(\'%\', :query, \'%\'))\n", nativeQuery=true) org.springframework.data.domain.Page<Product> findAllByFiltersAndQuery(Collection<String> sports, Collection<String> colors, Collection<String> features, Collection<String> countries, Collection<String> brands, Collection<Double> sizeUS, Collection<Double> sizeEUR, Collection<Double> sizeUK, @NotNull @NotNull BigDecimal minPrice, @NotNull @NotNull BigDecimal maxPrice, String query, org.springframework.data.domain.Pageable pageable)
